{"tid":2085653,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【佬訊專欄】杯弓Sir影 - 佬訊","createTime":"2020-06-30T03:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T03:36:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b9cbd14dcdda2d898338e92dbafd3956d1e81eb8","tid":2085653,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:33:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200630/UKKFPEXATJAKN6FE2G2MV5KBSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200630%2FUKKFPEXATJAKN6FE2G2MV5KBSY%2F&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=1f0f1d29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200630%2FUKKFPEXATJAKN6FE2G2MV5KBSY%2F&h=62a86dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200630/UKKFPEXATJAKN6FE2G2MV5KBSY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【佬訊專欄】杯弓Sir影 - 佬訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9VfQgu-2aidJgo-uIup8dc41keQ=/1280x940/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LP5EEAWNOBCUAMAQ2YCLVU4Z4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9VfQgu-2aidJgo-uIup8dc41keQ%3D%2F1280x940%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLP5EEAWNOBCUAMAQ2YCLVU4Z4Q.jpg&h=07202a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當警察連黃色頭盔飾物都容不下的時候，一件黃色Stutterheim雨褸，也可以出現「杯弓Sir影」。 互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n「我老公又發癲呀！」 <br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n一邊讀書，一邊聽阿儀的呻吟。<br />\n<br />\n阿儀是Peter的中學同學，身材標致，皮膚白皙，<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n，Peter也心裏有數，開始expect阿儀的電話及邀約。<br />\n<br />\n「你呢，記唔記得我有件黃色Stutterheim雨褸呀，呢，上次落雨出嚟我着過嘅呢。嗰件褸我當年grad trip喺瑞典買㗎，隻黃色好靚，好sharp，落雨着好搶眼㗎。」Peter靜靜地等重點。「佢呀，唔知發咩神經，噚日執衣櫃話要我掉咗佢！話橫掂都少着，唔好阻住，黐線，唔知佢個腦諗乜。」「咁都得？嗰件褸好靚㗎喎。」Peter其實大概估到阿儀老公的思路。當警察連黃色頭盔飾物都容不下的時候，他們的心理壓力，大概用「杯弓Sir影」也不足以形容。<br />\n<br />\n阿儀繼續呻了五分鐘，最後不忘嬌嗔一下，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n然後再返你度。不如就今個星期三？」<br />\n<br />\n佬訊<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/loshunhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Floshunhk%2F&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=43bd664e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/loshunhk/</a>"},{"pid":"3b84d60f8da2de355785d97288f5490726e847b0","tid":2085653,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7一維園見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzHhbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzHhbe.jpg&h=c0777e33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXtg54z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXtg54z.jpg&h=eae3d5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qizj3Rf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQizj3Rf.jpg&h=d33e105b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sg0OXbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSg0OXbk.jpg&h=791a8ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivfSEpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivfSEpG.jpg&h=e07fd1e0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}